  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>We're proud to say that the Chalet Isba is one of our properties run by our sister company Ski Total. Offering an authentic chalet experience in the Alps and with Sunday flying, we’re able to give you a greater choice and quality of chalets in <a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Meribel</a>.</strong></p>
<p>The chalet is a characterful property built into the hillside with views out across the Meribel valley. Set across four floors, the chalet's ten comfortable bedrooms all have en suite facilities. </p>
<p>Only a short walk away from the piste, guests have quick and easy access onto the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys Ski Area</a>. <span>There is also a ski bus stop just 100 m from the doorstep.</span></p>
<p>Guests can relax at the end of a day with a glass of wine in the chalet's private sauna, with picturesque mountain views from the decking. </p>
<p>Guests can alternatively enjoy the open plan living and dining area with open fireplace, in the games room or in the cinema room on the first floor. </p>]]></description>
